com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates
Class TemplateContext

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates.TemplateContext

public class TemplateContext
extends Object

The current state of a template. It contains two stacks: the template elements that are being processed and the currently executing actions.
